"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T21:19:57.000Z","msg":"好野嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  分清係人係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f315c7086ed8c1f225602f769abc4ae21301c70b","tid":268158,"uid":11601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T21:24:12.000Z","msg":"殘廢"},{"pid":"fecc3d28088f85d4cafed33cda5ee620cc5d2a83","tid":268158,"uid":108651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T22:40:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簡體字好醜<br />\n<br />\n只寫繁體 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得識繁體字係好值得驕傲既事<br />\n呢個文化需要好好珍惜同尊重 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係只寫繁體 我覺得簡體字根本就破壞緊中文字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5ad1c25eea4fb03d0acfe399956f426f4c199d","tid":268158,"uid":28966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T22:45:13.000Z","msg":"有種睇完好唔舒服既感覺<br />\n睇一段繁體字文如果要1分鐘<br />\n殘體字要用多一倍既時間"},{"pid":"586a38c053a67b6c8b3cbb6b470cce1e29157536","tid":268158,"uid":63482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T23:02:01.000Z","msg":"我閱讀無問題。<br />\n寫就唔太識寫，但急起上嚟如果要寫草稿都會撩咗啲似簡體既草字。<br />\n但認真使用文字時，一定係繁體，亦要警剔自己盡量避免用歐化中文(呢到用緊，因為唔知點形容比較貼切<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n始終香港人，要認清自己喺傳承中文正字文化嗰種獨特身份，因為我哋唔做，就唔會有人頂替我哋位置。"},{"pid":"b503c8b5ec494d6c13d8f8aa3f595ea43e565d73","tid":268158,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T23:06:16.000Z","msg":"原本目的係減少文盲同使人容易理解結果弄巧反拙 <br />\n不單止文盲沒有減少而且文章更令人難以理解<br />\n大陸已經白痴新加坡個牆頭草重要跟埋佢一齊癲<br />\n畀著係1941年嘅我肯定冇可能發生<br />\n可惜呢<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Y0ciQc8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FY0ciQc8.gif&h=6597160a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb2b5ada3435466939b1ee3fdebf5bbf756eaef3","tid":268158,"uid":110880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T00:16:52.000Z","msg":"屎"},{"pid":"0bebf9e0e915c84236b719afdae6c0ad46923d87","tid":268158,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T00:18:29.000Z","msg":"只寫正體"},{"pid":"61f7eec458fa5c2c6a66039bfdc8f26f2fa2331d","tid":268158,"uid":104513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T00:43:06.000Z","msg":"分辨低等人種既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea0fcdd763fe67402cf898cdbbb5c126a42c39e","tid":268158,"uid":13308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T00:45:42.000Z","msg":"低智商文字體"},{"pid":"224ed5b0fb38fc23747a30d32cac13806bd5ebec","tid":268158,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:46:38.000Z","msg":"當佢係唔正式既中文，就好似簡短版英文字句咁<br />\n例如c'mon=come on"},{"pid":"57d93da56ae7b7b0d4a4e7054afe495160489ebb","tid":268158,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:01:21.000Z","msg":"其實冇問題, 人地有人地用<br />\n我唔抗拒睇, 只係除左個&quot;體&quot;字, 都唔會用簡體"},{"pid":"c7220434ef14c2e7af907ec40e82d9ec44fcabaf","tid":268158,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:03:22.000Z","msg":"下等人種先會寫殘體字呢種反人類文明既文字"},{"pid":"cd952444137c230679cdcdb39c0491814e40d55f","tid":268158,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:09:14.000Z","msg":"繁體中文每隻字都有意思<br />\n但簡體啲字做唔到"},{"pid":"33b04c865f9a61037486ee10a9327e2c9e8311d3","tid":268158,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:09:16.000Z","msg":"殘體字同國史大綱一樣都係政治工具，甚至係為節省管治成本既虛構文明及愚民政策"},{"pid":"ee8d14503ca77604be2fda43367596e49c073707","tid":268158,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:09: